sequenceDiagram
    participant AI as AI Engine
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant CRUD as crud.create_event()
    participant DB as Database

    AI->>API: POST /api/v1/events (EventIn)
    API->>CRUD: create_event(db, payload)

    Note over CRUD,DB: Bước 1: Auto-create camera
    CRUD->>DB: SELECT camera by id
    alt Camera chưa tồn tại
        CRUD->>DB: INSERT cameras
    end

    Note over CRUD,DB: Bước 2: Tạo VehicleEvent
    CRUD->>DB: INSERT vehicle_events

    Note over CRUD,DB: Bước 3: Normalize plate_text
    CRUD->>CRUD: normalize_plate_text()

    Note over CRUD,DB: Bước 4: Tạo PlateRead
    CRUD->>DB: INSERT plate_reads

    Note over CRUD,DB: Bước 5: Auto-create Account
    CRUD->>DB: SELECT account by plate
    alt Account chưa tồn tại
        CRUD->>DB: INSERT accounts (balance=100,000)
        CRUD->>DB: INSERT transactions (type=init)
    end

    Note over CRUD,DB: Bước 6: Barrier decision
    CRUD->>CRUD: decide_barrier(status, direction)

    Note over CRUD,DB: Bước 7: Tạo BarrierAction + charge
    CRUD->>DB: INSERT barrier_actions
    CRUD->>DB: UPDATE accounts (balance -= 2,000)
    CRUD->>DB: INSERT transactions (type=event_charge)

    CRUD-->>API: (event, barrier_action)
    API-->>AI: EventOut JSON (barrier_action, registration_status)
